cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.AI 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with moth recognition from trap images using a descriptor that is robust to illumination changes and can detect and describe the external and internal contours of the target insect. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper uses a Support Vector Machine (SVM) classifier for classification. 
3. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is another possible category as the paper deals with image analysis and recognition. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with image analysis and recognition in the context of multimedia data. 
5. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with the development of an automatic algorithm for moth recognition.
